# InGop (Go+ language)

## One-stop Go+ programming language environment manager

<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://github.com/goplus/gop"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent." alt="" data-canonical-src="https://img.shields.io/badge/GoPlus-Programming%20Language-red?style=flat&amp;labelColor=white&amp;logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64," style="max-width: 100%;"></a>

How do I learn the **Go+** programming language quickly?

Start with installation, of course.
This repository **provides you with the environment** you need to install the **Go+** programming language with one click.

Not only that, you can **uninstall**, **fix** and **update** **Go+** with a single click.

Client Support: Mac/Windows/Linux
